<plot>A young man working at a used clothing shop in Osaka is infatuated with a young woman. When she finally says yes to his repeated requests, he is overjoyed, and his brightened attitude spreads to his co-workers. As the romance progresses and she comes to work at the shop with him, however, his relationship with his co-workers begins to strain and accusations of backstabbing and two-timing are thrown about. Is this really what he wanted?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?238717</url></doc>
